    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The ML surrogate achieves MAPE 2.3% and R² 0.974 on the held-out test set, with 100% correct RH classification. The 6 scoped-out factors are acceptable per ASME V&V 40-2018 at Model Risk Level 2. The surrogate is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device within the defined operating envelope.",
